Can He follow the footprints left behind by the Guardian God or Forge own damn legacy till the end?He is Smart, Calm, and Collected. Decisive during decision-making. He learns and grows. In the world of Humans, Monsters, and other unknown species. How is he going to overcome the challenges? and began his journey towards the Unknown.
